{"tid":2322314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去左西灣國殤紀念墳場","createTime":"2020-12-12T08:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T09:42:33.000Z","uid":105891,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"929c0f37ffd674e9bc4e7bce483e719fb0fd8e78","tid":2322314,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"今日第一次去，冇諗過咁多墓碑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比我想像中多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fepHfgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfepHfgq.png&h=8320611e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqWnfgv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqWnfgv.png&h=b0e3e845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住行落去8C，見到 J K Lawson 既墓碑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNddmW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNddmW3.png&h=080864c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係加軍犧牲既軍人中最高軍階<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日軍成功在港島登陸，並且誤打誤撞地進入了黃泥涌峽，向指揮部進迫。此時，西旅指揮部附近的部隊都被日軍圍困，羅遜只能等待皇家工兵連及由海軍組成的步兵前來解圍。可是到了第二天早上，皇家工兵亦被日軍在外圍阻擋，不能救出指揮部各人；上午10時，羅遜看著包圍的日軍越來越多，於是向莫德庇說：「<span class=\"red\">I am going outside to fight it out</span>.」，著手破壞重要文件及通訊設備後，就與指揮部的軍官、文員企圖殺出血路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然香港保衛戰唔止佢一個捐軀，牆上面仲有好多壯烈犧牲既軍人既名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hgsd6qk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgsd6qk.png&h=952ea6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhKHfiL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhKHfiL.png&h=479b86ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有好多無名英雄既墓碑，佢哋好多廿歲左右就戰死沙場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一生都返唔到家鄉，有種古來征戰幾人回既感慨<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒去獻花，或者向佢地salute, 或者講句thank you 去紀念一班曾經為香港這片土地奉獻過既烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總覺得香港人欠佢哋一句多謝"},{"pid":"de1acd7e53ed9bd553f4fab68087a6456c49b11b","tid":2322314,"uid":45977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"lest we forget<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b834b6f72d713a1d759c582d57f69b3a549a05b","tid":2322314,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"為香港而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdc3c1e2dc47b13cae30d0e9d3e4142c5937a30","tid":2322314,"uid":105891,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b834b6f72d713a1d759c582d57f69b3a549a05b","tid":2322314,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"為香港而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"令我諗起上年既部份香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />異曲同工"},{"pid":"a6c045673ee1559b7c0987f8960138dd31988ce8","tid":2322314,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46588e618f3b0babf4f55c241840f6c71405d037","tid":2322314,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b83269109200a636314a5d5e7652a919ba212f6","tid":2322314,"uid":247892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}